    <h2>About Us</h2>
    <p>Welcome to our Library Management System, a comprehensive solution designed to streamline book borrowing and management processes for modern libraries.</p>

    <h3>Our Mission</h3>
    <p>We aim to provide an efficient, user-friendly platform that makes library operations seamless for both staff and patrons. Our system digitizes traditional library processes, reducing paperwork and improving accessibility.</p>

    <h3>Key Features</h3>
    <p>Our system offers complete book inventory management with detailed location tracking through sections and rack IDs. The borrowing system automatically tracks due dates and returns, ensuring smooth operations. Real-time availability status helps users quickly find books they need.</p>

    <h3>Technology</h3>
    <p>Built with ASP.NET Core Web API backend and modern web technologies, our system ensures reliability, security, and performance. The RESTful API architecture allows for easy integration and scalability.</p>

